{"type":null,"faqId":49994,"title":"如何在照片中添加地理位置信息？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body1415990\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264236__p51480007\">在拍照界面，打开菜单选项，点击“设置”，打开“地理位置”开关。同时保证GPS是开启状态。</p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264236__note60666882\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d31_atho4.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264236__p12743916\">室内GPS相比室外而言，定位不准或无法定位，需要移动数据网络来辅助定位，因此在室内拍照，需要手机联网才能定位照片的地理位置。</p><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264236__p47586383\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d32_fc598.jpg\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264236","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627735000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"照片,地理信息","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}